data.description: This end unit with no thru traffic boasts a wraparound fenced yard with a 3rd parking stall for a compact car! The open concept home offers private bathrooms, the primary with double sinks, and a bonus laundry room that makes it convenient for you. Live the Kapolei lifestyle with everything you need, Ka Makana Ali’I Mall, Costco, Dining, Entertainment, Ko’Olina Resort, and more. Or take a stroll to the Mehana Community Center that offers a pool, bbq area, and fitness room! Mehana also offers a dog park, playgrounds, convenience stores, salons and spas, also a bike path. Live, Work, and Play in Kapolei! OPEN SUN 1/14, 1-4PM.
